<br>
This is coming from someone whose highest tradeskill is smithing (1) which I got combining my potc earring.<br>
<br>
Anyways, got a few questions:<br>
<br>
1) Is pottery easy to raise?  Can it be done with only vendor items or is it necessary to farm lots of crap?<br>
<br>
2) Does it matter what race/religion I am for pottery?  Are there items that can be created only by certain races or followers of certain deities?<br>
<br>
3) Do I need other tradeskills to skill up in pottery (to make intermediate products)?<br>
<br>
